com.starsoft.plib.core.commands

Class ExecutorCommands.ShutdownNow

  • com.starsoft.plib.core.commands.ExecutorCommands.ShutdownNow
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Processor<T,V>
    Enclosing class:
    ExecutorCommands

    public static class ExecutorCommands.ShutdownNow
implements Processor<T,V>

    When passing an instance of this class as parameter "processor" to com.starsoft.plib.core.interfaces.ProcessorExecutor.processing in implementation of interface ProcessorExecutor the executor stops working Attempts to stop all actively executing tasks, halts the processing of waiting tasks, and returns a list of the tasks that were awaiting execution in the onProcessedCallback call if it is presented. These tasks are drained (removed) from the task queue. the instance of interface ProcessorExecutor will be stopped and cannot be used in the future

    See Also:
    com.starsoft.plib.core.interfaces.ProcessorExecutor.processing, interface ProcessorExecutor, interface ProcessorExecutor

      • ShutdownNow

        public ShutdownNow()

        usually not required
